  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_10",
    "text": "FROM BACK PAGE that the different Puma match ball in the competition played a part because it is different to what they are used to in the Premier League. The Gunners boss said: \"We kicked a lot of balls over the bar, and it's tricky that these balls fly a lot so there's details that we can do better.",
