    "order": 15
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_16",
    "text": "Howe said: \"Alex played very well in the first half today, he looked really good physically, his pace and movements were giving them a problem. I was delighted with how he performed.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.38881411694332285,
      0.6857142857142857,
      0.5580978017048004,
      0.7440329218106996
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 16
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_18",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.036488709436219534,
      0.6894767783656672,
      0.16031105129355466,
      0.8512639623750735
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 17
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_13",
    "text": "\"It's just half-time. When I see the team play, and how we deal with a lot of situations and play against a very good team I must say I have full belief that we can go out there and do it.\"",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.2069687453267534,
      0.6946502057613169,
      0.3768506056527591,
      0.7534391534391535
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 18
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_17",
    "text": "\"\"When Alex is in that mood, as he was in the first half, he is a brilliant player for us. It goes without saying that he does the hard work and raises our overall level.\"",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.38881411694332285,
      0.7445032333921223,
      0.5616868550919695,
      0.7929453262786597
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 19
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_14",
    "text": "Isak scored his 1Oth goal in nine games (celebrating, above) and his strike partner Gordon claimed: \"! don't think there's a better centre forward in Europe at the moment.\" Newcastle boss Eddie Howe hailed his team's performance and also that of danger man Isak.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.20816509645580977,
      0.7539094650205761,
      0.37027067444294903,
      0.7929453262786597
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 20
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_20",
    "text": "®",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.480933153880664,
      0.8051734273956496,
      0.5234036189621654,
      0.8348030570252792
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 21
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_30",
    "text": "Alexander Isak took his chance while Arsenal's forward line wasted every opening. It is now 50 goals for Isak in all competitions since he joined Newcastle for £63million in August 2022.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5329744279946165,
      0.8098765432098766,
      0.6735456856587408,
      0.8884185773074662
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 22
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_33",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
