  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_26",
    "text": "BY JOHN CROSS Chief Football Writer X@johncrossmirror",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3858232391206819,
      0.8103468547912992,
      0.47315687154179753,
      0.8343327454438566
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 25
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_25",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1788544937939285,
      0.8108171663727219,
      0.3810378346044564,
      0.975896531452087
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 26
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_27",
    "text": "THE Toon Army are already singing about Wembley.",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.3858232391206819,
      0.83668430335097,
      0.5257963212202782,
      0.8667842445620223
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 27
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_38",
    "text": "The squad looks wafer-thin and they lack a proven goals- corer. As good as Kai Havertz was last season, the Arsenal striker horribly mistimed a second-half header (far right) and a chance to haul his team back into the tie.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.82907133243607,
      0.8493827160493828,
      0.9690444145356663,
      0.9274544385655497
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 28
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_21",
    "text": "ALEXANDER ISAK Scored one, had a hand in the other",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.04725586959772693,
      0.8531452087007643,
      0.14894571556751907,
      0.8813639035861258
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 29
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_28",
    "text": "And no wonder. Newcastle have got one foot in the Carabao Cup final on March 16 after a hugely impressive display at the Emirates.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3858232391206819,
      0.867254556143445,
      0.52519814565575,
      0.9166372721928278
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 30
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_34",
    "text": "Even more worryingly, they have hit the wall at just the wrong time.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6819201435621355,
      0.8700764256319812,
      0.8218932256617317,
      0.8978248089359201
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 31
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_31",
    "text": "He is the reason why they are dreaming of their first major trophy in 56 years.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5335726035591446,
      0.8888888888888888,
      0.6723493345296845,
      0.9180482069370959
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 32
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_22",
    "text": "NEXT THREE...",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.03768506056527591,
      0.8931216931216931,
      0.10527889935696126,
      0.9058201058201059
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 33
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_35",
    "text": "They face Manchester United in the FA Cup third round on Sunday and are already six points behind Liverpool in the title race, having played a game more.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6807237924330791,
      0.8982951205173427,
      0.8212950500972035,
      0.957554379776602
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 34
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_23",
    "text": "ARSENAL",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.03768506056527591,
      0.9072310405643739,
      0.06699566322715717,
      0.9138154027042916
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 35
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_24",
    "text": "Sun Man United (home).AC Wed Tottenham (home)…PL Jan 18 Aston Vila(home)…PL NEWCASTLE Sun Bromley (home)……FAC Wed Wolves (home)…PL Jan 18 Bournemouth (home)…PL - 0 -",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.03768506056527591,
      0.9142857142857143,
      0.1579183490354419,
      0.9711934156378601
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 36
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_29",
    "text": "Eddie Howe's men looked sharp, slick and dangerous while Arsenal were horribly flat with their season now in serious danger of fading away. In truth, it was al about the",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3858232391206819,
      0.9166372721928278,
      0.52519814565575,
      0.975896531452087
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 37
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_32",
    "text": "Isak even played a part in Newcastle's second goal as it was his cross shot which led to Anthony Gordon (left) firing in the rebound to give them a huge advantage for a minor miracle to turn the semi-final on its head in next month's return, but they look ragged, tired and as if they are running on empty.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5335726035591446,
      0.9180482069370959,
      0.6735456856587408,
      0.9773074661963551
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 38
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_39",
    "text": "That miss summed up Arsenal's shortcomings. They were wasteful in attack, sloppy in defence and lacking ideas in midfield. They racked",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.82907133243607,
      0.9279247501469724,
      0.9690444145356663,
      0.9773074661963551
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 39
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_36",
    "text": "Arsenal are still in the Champions League, but they threat and quality with Bukayo Saka out injured for the next two months.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6813219679976072,
      0.9580246913580247,
      0.8212950500972035,
      0.9768371546149324
    ],
